Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases where the next activity is 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time until 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' is performed after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled' without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time it takes from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Payment Handled' in successful claims
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases where rejection occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases successfully concluding with 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'
